{"tid":816630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"預言家朱瑟里諾：有關強颱風「山竹」之預測","createTime":"2018-09-13T01:00:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T10:15:57.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ed132b37386e1797a25eea9c6e85cfca8ee301e8","tid":816630,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:00:18.000Z","msg":"朱瑟里諾早在2017年12月於「澳門群組年度聚會」時提及，香港和澳門於2018年8月至9月期間將會遇上強颱風吹襲，對澳門造成極大破壞；又於2018年7月15日和8月8日分別在其國際官網（<a href=\"http://www.jucelinoluz.com.br/2018/07/15/copa-na-russia-poucos-incidentes-vulcao-no-chile-sao-os-pressagios-da-semana/）、亞洲區官網（www.jnl-asia.com/blog/posts/20180808-typhoon-forecast）及Facebook專頁（9月環球預測\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jucelinoluz.com.br%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2Fcopa-na-russia-poucos-incidentes-vulcao-no-chile-sao-os-pressagios-da-semana%2F%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%8D%80%E5%AE%98%E7%B6%B2%EF%BC%88www.jnl-asia.com%2Fblog%2Fposts%2F20180808-typhoon-forecast%EF%BC%89%E5%8F%8AFacebook%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81%EF%BC%889%E6%9C%88%E7%92%B0%E7%90%83%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC&d=qrZihtvkcViWUrD%2FnB6oPdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=e9dae915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.jucelinoluz.com.br/2018/07/15/copa-na-russia-poucos-incidentes-vulcao-no-chile-sao-os-pressagios-da-semana/）、亞洲區官網（www.jnl-asia.com/blog/posts/20180808-typhoon-forecast）及Facebook專頁（9月環球預測</a> - 第15項，<a href=\"https://www.jucelinodaluz.com.br/previsoes/641-previsoes-para-setembro-de-2018-por-jucelino-luz）發佈稱，有一股強颱風將於2018年9月14日吹襲香港和澳門，呼籲各位做好防風準備，尤其是居住在低漥地區的人。經朱瑟里諾證實，這個強颱風便是「山竹」。以下是朱瑟里諾於2018年1月9日寄給南卡羅來納州州長的一封預言信，當中提及有關「山竹」更詳細的資訊。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jucelinodaluz.com.br%2Fprevisoes%2F641-previsoes-para-setembro-de-2018-por-jucelino-luz%EF%BC%89%E7%99%BC%E4%BD%88%E7%A8%B1%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E8%82%A1%E5%BC%B7%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E5%B0%87%E6%96%BC2018%E5%B9%B49%E6%9C%8814%E6%97%A5%E5%90%B9%E8%A5%B2%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%92%8C%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E5%90%84%E4%BD%8D%E5%81%9A%E5%A5%BD%E9%98%B2%E9%A2%A8%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%A4%E5%85%B6%E6%98%AF%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%9C%A8%E4%BD%8E%E6%BC%A5%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%82%E7%B6%93%E6%9C%B1%E7%91%9F%E9%87%8C%E8%AB%BE%E8%AD%89%E5%AF%A6%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%99%E5%80%8B%E5%BC%B7%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E4%BE%BF%E6%98%AF%E3%80%8C%E5%B1%B1%E7%AB%B9%E3%80%8D%E3%80%82%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%B1%E7%91%9F%E9%87%8C%E8%AB%BE%E6%96%BC2018%E5%B9%B41%E6%9C%889%E6%97%A5%E5%AF%84%E7%B5%A6%E5%8D%97%E5%8D%A1%E7%BE%85%E4%BE%86%E7%B4%8D%E5%B7%9E%E5%B7%9E%E9%95%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%B0%81%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%80%E4%BF%A1%EF%BC%8C%E7%95%B6%E4%B8%AD%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%8A%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C%E3%80%8C%E5%B1%B1%E7%AB%B9%E3%80%8D%E6%9B%B4%E8%A9%B3%E7%B4%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A%E3%80%82&d=qrZihtvkcViWUrD%2FnB6oPdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=28adc85a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.jucelinodaluz.com.br/previsoes/641-previsoes-para-setembro-de-2018-por-jucelino-luz）發佈稱，有一股強颱風將於2018年9月14日吹襲香港和澳門，呼籲各位做好防風準備，尤其是居住在低漥地區的人。經朱瑟里諾證實，這個強颱風便是「山竹」。以下是朱瑟里諾於2018年1月9日寄給南卡羅來納州州長的一封預言信，當中提及有關「山竹」更詳細的資訊。</a><br />\n<br />\n《信件重點內容翻譯》<br />\n<br />\n致南卡羅來納州州長亨利：<br />\n<br />\n1. 颶風佛羅倫斯將可能於2018年9月13日吹襲南卡羅來納州東岸地區，其風眼將集結於百慕達群島和巴哈馬群島之間，並將於2018年9月13日至14日在北卡羅來納州和南部的邊界上登陸，雖然它的移動路徑仍在變化中，颶風強度可達4至5級，沿海地區將可能受到吹襲，如的地區包括，如Topsail島嶼海灘、弗吉尼亞州，以及北部更遠的地區。此外，熱帶風暴艾薩克（Isaac）和颶風海倫（Helene）也會出現在大西洋之上。<br />\n<br />\n2. 第23號颱風將於2018年9月11日形成，並將命名為百里嘉（Barijat），這意味著馬紹爾群島沿海地區將受到影響。在2018年9月14日至16日期間，它將在南海向西移動，並朝向越南或中國。另一方面，第22號颱風將靠近馬里亞納群島，並將不斷增強，於2018年9月13日吹襲日本。<br />\n<br />\n3. 澳洲女演員及歌手奧利維&middot;紐頓 - 約翰（Olivia Newton-John）因其在音樂劇中扮演的角色而聞名，她可能第三次患上癌症，是次患癌位置為脊柱底部發現腫瘤，必須接受放射治療。朱瑟里諾曾於1991年向她發出一封信件，告知她於1992年將可能患上乳腺癌，並能克服該癌症；同時，朱瑟里諾也告知奧利維將於2013年被診斷出肩膊患有腫瘤。她會感到情緒激動，所以需要特別注意情緒的問題。<br />\n<br />\n4. 颱風山竹（Mangkhut）將持續增強，並於2018年9月11日繼續接近菲律賓地區，這股強大的颱風也將吹襲澳門、台灣和中國香港，但澳門部分地區將會十分危險，如Dawuwan、珠海、Dawan Bay、Biqingwan碧清灣（如在這地區沒有發生狀況，今年內還是有可能受影響的）。同時，颱風Ompong也將於南呂宋島的東部形成，並於2018年9月15日威脅北呂宋島、可能横越巴丹群島省。它使西南季候風增強，並為三寶顏半島、西米沙鄢群島和巴拉望島帶來零散的中度降雨和雷暴。<br />\n<br />\n朱瑟里諾教授<br />\n《翻譯完》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2209228442440549&amp;id=131442050219209&amp;_ft_=top_level_post_id.2209228442440549%3Atl_objid.2209228442440549%3Acontent_owner_id_new.131442050219209%3Athrowback_story_fbid.2209228442440549%3Apage_id.131442050219209%3Aphoto_id.2209224502440943%3Apage_insights.%7B%22131442050219209%22%3A%7B%22role%22%3A1%2C%22page_id%22%3A131442050219209%2C%22post_context%22%3A%7B%22story_fbid%22%3A2209228442440549%2C%22publish_time%22%3A1536732848%2C%22story_name%22%3A%22EntStatusCreationStory%22%2C%22object_fbtype%22%3A266%7D%2C%22actor_id%22%3A131442050219209%2C%22psn%22%3A%22EntStatusCreationStory%22%2C%22sl%22%3A4%2C%22dm%22%3A%7B%22isShare%22%3A0%2C%22originalPostOwnerID%22%3A0%7D%2C%22targets%22%3A%5B%7B%22page_id%22%3A131442050219209%2C%22actor_id%22%3A131442050219209%2C%22role%22%3A1%2C%22post_id%22%3A2209228442440549%2C%22share_id%22%3A0%7D%5D%7D%7D&amp;__tn__=%2As%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2209228442440549%26id%3D131442050219209%26_ft_%3Dtop_level_post_id.2209228442440549%253Atl_objid.2209228442440549%253Acontent_owner_id_new.131442050219209%253Athrowback_story_fbid.2209228442440549%253Apage_id.131442050219209%253Aphoto_id.2209224502440943%253Apage_insights.%257B%2522131442050219209%2522%253A%257B%2522role%2522%253A1%252C%2522page_id%2522%253A131442050219209%252C%2522post_context%2522%253A%257B%2522story_fbid%2522%253A2209228442440549%252C%2522publish_time%2522%253A1536732848%252C%2522story_name%2522%253A%2522EntStatusCreationStory%2522%252C%2522object_fbtype%2522%253A266%257D%252C%2522actor_id%2522%253A131442050219209%252C%2522psn%2522%253A%2522EntStatusCreationStory%2522%252C%2522sl%2522%253A4%252C%2522dm%2522%253A%257B%2522isShare%2522%253A0%252C%2522originalPostOwnerID%2522%253A0%257D%252C%2522targets%2522%253A%255B%257B%2522page_id%2522%253A131442050219209%252C%2522actor_id%2522%253A131442050219209%252C%2522role%2522%253A1%252C%2522post_id%2522%253A2209228442440549%252C%2522share_id%2522%253A0%257D%255D%257D%257D%26__tn__%3D%252As%252As-R&d=qrZihtvkcViWUrD%2FnB6oPdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=357b4f9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2209228442440549&amp;id=131442050219209&amp;_ft_=top_level_post_id.2209228442440549%3Atl_objid.2209228442440549%3Acontent_owner_id_new.131442050219209%3Athrowback_story_fbid.2209228442440549%3Apage_id.131442050219209%3Aphoto_id.2209224502440943%3Apage_insights.%7B%22131442050219209%22%3A%7B%22role%22%3A1%2C%22page_id%22%3A131442050219209%2C%22post_context%22%3A%7B%22story_fbid%22%3A2209228442440549%2C%22publish_time%22%3A1536732848%2C%22story_name%22%3A%22EntStatusCreationStory%22%2C%22object_fbtype%22%3A266%7D%2C%22actor_id%22%3A131442050219209%2C%22psn%22%3A%22EntStatusCreationStory%22%2C%22sl%22%3A4%2C%22dm%22%3A%7B%22isShare%22%3A0%2C%22originalPostOwnerID%22%3A0%7D%2C%22targets%22%3A%5B%7B%22page_id%22%3A131442050219209%2C%22actor_id%22%3A131442050219209%2C%22role%22%3A1%2C%22post_id%22%3A2209228442440549%2C%22share_id%22%3A0%7D%5D%7D%7D&amp;__tn__=%2As%2As-R</a>"},{"pid":"7796eae0e5f23327235e46f3fa375905f6b40c09","tid":816630,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:09:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c7b244067530ba308435b2ac50f6177c5168b0","tid":816630,"uid":23707,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:14:56.000Z","msg":"點解澳門同台灣唔加中國？屌你"},{"pid":"7cc54a5eac4e885e12fb6eff801ebed1be8c4849","tid":816630,"uid":63909,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:17:37.000Z","msg":"香港和澳門於<del>2018年</del>8月至9月期間將會遇上強颱風吹襲<br />\n<br />\nDLLM<br />\nONL99<br />\n邊年會無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dfe3c87a3eec4f73156402ba809d90f4e14c503","tid":816630,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:41:33.000Z","msg":"超級神棍，有人信果下慘"},{"pid":"6e9b6b119ac873b2eb8ba3ed2de41954e780ecb2","tid":816630,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://shoplineimg.com/594e8f5a59d5241745001cdf/59e30588552115421b005e6e/1200x.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshoplineimg.com%2F594e8f5a59d5241745001cdf%2F59e30588552115421b005e6e%2F1200x.jpg%3F&h=a189230e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">朱瑟里諾教授｜現今最有公信力、預言準繩度最高的預言家</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n朱瑟里諾。達。盧茲（Jucelino Nobrega da Luz，1960年3月7日，下稱朱瑟里諾）是巴西預言家、環保主義者和寫作家。他生於巴西弗洛里亞努，在大學時期主修哲學與文采（Philosophy and Letters），也曾在米納斯吉拉斯州擔任教師。現與太太和四子女居住在聖保羅市沃特斯林德諾（&Aacute;guas de Lind&oacute;ia）。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n第一個「預知夢」<br />\n<br />\n朱瑟里諾自九歲就能從睡夢中看見未來影像，那些夢被稱為「預知夢」（premonitory dream）。他的第一個預知夢發生於1969年某天晚上，當時他看見一個四人家庭在巴西著名高速公路Anchieta駕駛時發生嚴重交通意外，全部罹難。不幸的，該「夢境」在四年後（即1972年）竟然成真，自此朱瑟里諾的父母也得承認其兒子擁有著這份「上天賦予的禮物」。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n預見世界性事件<br />\n<br />\n十三歲起，朱瑟里諾在「預知夢」中看到的事情越來越多，當中更涉及多宗世界性的大事件及天然災禍，例如王妃戴安娜車禍事件、911恐怖襲擊、印尼蘇門答臘大地震和海嘯（南亞海嘯）、蘇聯貝斯蘭人質事件、羅馬法王若望保祿二世逝世、日本昭和天皇逝世、阪神淡路 7.2 級大地震、東京地下鐵沙林毒氣事件、薩達姆和拉登的隱藏地點、奧巴馬當選美國總統、米高積遜之死、四川大地震、311日本仙台大地震、菲律賓人質事件及發現世紀病菌禽流感（H1N1）及豬流感（H5N1）等等......。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n預言信<br />\n<br />\n每當從「預知夢」收到「信息」，朱瑟里諾便將「信息」寫成預言信件，內容包括「未來事件」發生之年、月、日，寄予與相關人士，望其能避過災難或協助減低因天災人禍帶來的傷亡。所有「預言信」寄出前均獲當地公證事務處核實、登記，以便公眾查證；並且保留郵寄收據，以作記錄。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n預言非宿命<br />\n<br />\n過去四十年間，朱瑟里諾曾預言的事件超過十萬件，命中率高達七成，成為現今最有公信力，命中率極高的預言家。即使如此，朱瑟里諾卻認為「預知夢」非「宿命」，我們只要付諸行動，做好事前準備，未來是可以改變的！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.jnl-asia.com/pages/jucelino-nobrega-da-luz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jnl-asia.com%2Fpages%2Fjucelino-nobrega-da-luz&d=qrZihtvkcViWUrD%2FnB6oPdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=130218a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.jnl-asia.com/pages/jucelino-nobrega-da-luz</a>"},{"pid":"f5e15edccdb22c69241f611a15f41adb46d4c626","tid":816630,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:00:53.000Z","msg":"有無夢見冰冰 接客先"},{"pid":"9ddb7d4eeedd4c2af2bd7bdbfdbc49b180065b06","tid":816630,"uid":80072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:00:54.000Z","msg":"中你老母閪個國"},{"pid":"ce3521260078379b5aa4fffa811a4de2e80b418a","tid":816630,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03c7b244067530ba308435b2ac50f6177c5168b0","tid":816630,"uid":23707,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:14:56.000Z","msg":"點解澳門同台灣唔加中國？屌你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:30:00.000Z","msg":"中國山竹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2355ddc338bc5943eb22228aafa3e981cbbaf706","tid":816630,"uid":34223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:46:18.000Z","msg":"預言家指出 人被殺就會死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb8873908cd587a07109e32f14855caffe66d4f","tid":816630,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:47:41.000Z","msg":"2018-6=2012<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7bee3c2c3d6863fe4b30ca79ba42752ff2b80f","tid":816630,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 台獨澳獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5679d517276a0f76ed348436edc0a4b5709b70db","tid":816630,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T03:01:37.000Z","msg":"2. 第23號颱風將於2018年9月11日形成，並將命名為百里嘉（Barijat），這意味著馬紹爾群島沿海地區將受到影響。在2018年9月14日至16日期間，它將在南海向西移動，並朝向越南或中國。另一方面，第22號颱風將靠近馬里亞納群島，並將不斷增強，於2018年9月13日